title._content: Lane Block, Main Street, Keene NH

description._content: TITLE Lane Block, Main Street, Keene NH CREATOR Keene Camera Club SUBJECT Business districts - NH - Keene Central business districts Stores and shops - NH - Keene Buildings - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION Photograph of the E.F. Lane Block, east side of Main Street, Keene New Hampshire, around 1900, showing Yeates' Department Store. 26-32 Main Street. "The brick buildings erected by Elisha F. Lane on land between Cheshire House and Church Street....Elisha F. Lane bought the property in 1890 from Brigham Nims and built the present brick block. " PUBLISHER Keene Public Library DATE DIGITAL 20080509 DATE ORIGINAL 1900?
